Clause Text: Access To Training Area – The Company shall maintain a Training Area that may include lessons, forms, worksheets, checklists, and other information. You shall have access to this Training Area for a period of {program_area_access_period}.

Clause Text: Access To Private Discussion Group – The Company shall maintain a Private Group that You will have access to as a member of the Program. You will have access to the Private Group for a period of {program_group_access_period}. That Group provides a forum for You to connect with other Program participants and seek guidance and support. Members of the Company will seek to interact with Program participants in the group, but the Company does not make any guarantees about participation by any of its employees, founders, or members in the Group. You are required to abide by any and all rules posted in that Group. If You fail to abide by those rules, You will forfeit Your right to participate in that Group. In the event You lose Your right to participate in the Group as a result of rules violation, You shall not receive a refund.
Clause Help: This sets out that the company will provide customers with access to a private discussion community as part of the program. It provides a limit on how long customers will have access and also gives the company the right to remove them if they cause trouble.

Clause Text: One-On-One Calls – Program participants are entitled to {program_individual_call_count} calls with coaches and/or consultants working for the Company. Similarly, You may not cancel or reschedule a call unless You do so at least {program_individual_call_rescheduling_period} hours in advance.

Clause Text: Bonuses – From time to time, the Company may offer bonuses to individuals who sign up for the Program. You shall be entitled to any bonuses offered to You at the time of registration.

Delete Warning: If you ever include bonuses that only some buyers get access to, you should include this section.

Clause Text: The Virtual Bootcamp – The Company will hold a virtual bootcamp on {virtual_bootcamp_date}, which will include live instruction, implementation time, and the ability to receive feedback from the Company’s employees and agents. You will be able to stream the live instruction and engage in the interactive elements through a platform designed to facilitate such virtual interactions. The Company will provide information about the preferred technical requirements to use the platform closer to the event. It is Your sole responsibility to ensure that You have a computer or other electronic device that will allow You to access the virtual platform.
Clause Help: This clause sets out the details of the bootcamp itself. The company should make sure the description of what will happen is accurate. The company can modify this clause by removing elements that don't apply.
